OL,3,CHospital under 'extreme' pressure as
OL,4,Cpatients face 15-hour wait in A&E
OL,6,FOne of Wales' largest emergency
OL,7,Fdepartments currently has a 15-hour
OL,8,Fwait, with the health board urging
OL,9,Fpatients with minor injuries to find
OL,10,Ftreatment elsewhere.
OL,12,Fsaid that faces "extreme" pressures,
OL,13,Fwith "very high numbers of patients
OL,14,Fwho are extremely unwell".
OL,16,FIt comes after the hospital declared a
OL,17,F"Black Alert" earlier this week - the
OL,18,Fhighest level of escalation meaning it
OL,19,Ffaces exceptional demand.
