OL,3,CHospital under 'extreme' pressure as
OL,4,Cpatients face 15-hour wait in A&E
OL,6,FThe health board has advised patients
OL,7,Fwith only minor injuries - such as
OL,8,Fcuts, burns, sprains, strains,
OL,9,Fdislocations and broken bones - to go
OL,10,Fto the Minor Injury Unit (MIU) at
OL,11,FHospital, which only has a 15-minute
OL,12,Fwait.
OL,14,F"We are seeing very high numbers of
OL,15,Fpatients who are extremely unwell,"
OL,16,Fthe health board said.
